query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 t1 tq1 s) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('drivers',
'installation',
'lubuntu',
'system-installation',
'xubuntu')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Announcer',
'Enlightened',
'Enthusiast',
'Favorite Question',
'Good Answer',
'Great Answer',
'Great Question',
'Guru',
'Investor',
'Organizer',
'Peer Pressure',
'Suffrage')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
